def paper_regulariser(weights): norm = tf.sqrt(tf.reduce_sum(tf.square(weights), axis=0, keepdims=True)) assert norm.shape == [1, 12] normalised_weights = weights / norm dot_prod_between_topic_matrices = tf.matmul(normalised_weights, tf.transpose(normalised_weights)) return dot_prod_between_topic_matrices
